00:30:23,363 --> 00:30:24,531
you know, for the English.

576
00:30:24,698 --> 00:30:26,658
And she's very naive,
doesn't know much.

577
00:30:26,825 --> 00:30:28,035
Because that's how she would be.

578
00:30:28,201 --> 00:30:30,704
