594
00:31:25,175 --> 00:31:27,094
Which sounds ridiculous,
but of course,

595
00:31:27,260 --> 00:31:29,262
today, India like
any other country,

596
00:31:29,429 --> 00:31:35,227
there is a huge proponent
towards polyester.

597
00:31:35,394 --> 00:31:40,440
Anything that's easy to
wash and easy to dry.

